title: `$file->consent()`
description: Set file permission.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
->consent($consent);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
File::open('path\to\file.txt')->consent(0600);
~~~

Shortcut to set file permission during saving:

~~~ .php
File::set('test!')->saveTo('path\to\file.txt', 0600);
~~~

~~~ .php
File::open('path\to\file.txt')->set('test!')->save(0600);
~~~